Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: lernstick-libreoffice-math
Architecture: all
Depends: libreoffice-math
Description: Removes the LibreOffice Math menu entry
 We remove the LibreOffice Math menu entry because we already have
 the LibreOffice menu entry for the whole office suite.
 We also enforce the GNOME user interface because the file dialog in the KDE
 user interface currently just sucks.
 See https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=752230 for details.
 We also add a workaround for the following bug:
 https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=798591
